<p>All lines in a text file should be removed if matching the pattern xxx unless the line contains yyy</p>  <p>Example input:</p>  <pre> - 1 This first line does not contain the pattern. - 2 This second line does contain the pattern xxx but still can't be deleted because of yyy. - 3 This thirth line should be remove because it only contains xxx. </pre>  <p>The desired output:</p>  <pre>  - 1 This first line does not contain the pattern. - 2 This second line does contain the pattern xxx but still can't be deleted because of yyy. </pre>